commit_message:
implement sql and kvs backend for 'GET /users/{user_id}/roles'

fix bug #933565

The interface will return a list of roles granted to the user,
with tenant info which the role is associated with.

Response  :
{
    "roles": [
        {
            "id": "1",
            "name": "admin",
            "tenantName": "demo",
            "tenantId": "111"
        },
